{"title":"BigData-Hadoop","slug":"BigData-Hadoop","date":"2023-03-06","updated":"2023-03-22","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/30565.json","excerpt":"<blockquote><p> 主要介绍了大数据中 Hadoop 集群的使用 </p></blockquote>","cover":null,"covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>主要介绍了大数据中 Hadoop 集群的使用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1 id=\"时间同步\"><a href=\"# 时间同步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"时间同步\"></a>时间同步 </h1><h2 id=\"分节点\"><a href=\"# 分节点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分节点\"></a> 分节点</h2><blockquote>\n<p>在 3 个 slave 节点上执行命令【service ntpd stop】、【ntpdate master】、【service ntpd start &amp; chkconfig ntpd on】启动与主节点 master 的时间同步服务。 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"主节点\"><a href=\"# 主节点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主节点\"></a>主节点</h2><blockquote>\n<p>在主节点执行 /usr/local/sbin/ 目录下的命令【ntp_update】，可快速启动时间同步服务。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"集群的启动与关闭\"><a href=\"# 集群的启动与关闭\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"集群的启动与关闭\"></a>集群的启动与关闭 </h1><h2 id=\"启动\"><a href=\"# 启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动\"></a> 启动</h2><blockquote>\n<p>执行 /usr/local/sbin/hadoop_cluster.start 即可</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"关闭\"><a href=\"# 关闭\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"关闭\"></a>关闭</h2><blockquote>\n<p>执行 /usr/local/sbin/hadoop_cluster stop 即可</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"Hadoop 集群的操作\"><a href=\"#Hadoop 集群的操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hadoop 集群的操作\"></a>Hadoop 集群的操作 </h1><h2 id=\"查看节点进程\"><a href=\"# 查看节点进程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看节点进程\"></a> 查看节点进程</h2><blockquote>\n<p>/usr/local/sbin/hadoop_cluster status</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"查看当前主机名\"><a href=\"# 查看当前主机名\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看当前主机名\"></a>查看当前主机名</h2><blockquote>\n<p>hostname : 查看当前主机全名<br>hostname -f : 查找当前主机配置的映射名</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"Web 界面操作 Hadoop\"><a href=\"#Web 界面操作 Hadoop\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web 界面操作 Hadoop\"></a>Web 界面操作 Hadoop</h1><h2 id=\"HDFS 监控\"><a href=\"#HDFS 监控\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HDFS 监控\"></a>HDFS 监控</h2><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://master:50070/\">http://master:50070</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"应用监控\"><a href=\"# 应用监控\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"应用监控\"></a>应用监控</h2><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://master:8080/\">http://master:8080</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","url":"/posts/30565/","min2read":"1","word4post":184,"prev_post":{"title":"BigData-HDFS","url":"/posts/32491/"},"next_post":{"title":"JavaStream","url":"/posts/44747/"},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"时间同步\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">时间同步 </span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"分节点\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\"> 分节点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"主节点\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">主节点</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"集群的启动与关闭\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">集群的启动与关闭 </span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"启动\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\"> 启动</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"关闭\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">关闭</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"Hadoop 集群的操作\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">Hadoop 集群的操作 </span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"查看节点进程\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\"> 查看节点进程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"查看当前主机名\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.2.</span> <span cla